dct_title_s: The valleys of the Tibagy & Ivahy, Province of the Paraná, South Brazil
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Mountain ranges and Indian [indigenous] territories are labeled. Carriage roads, mule tracks, and boundaries of forest and prairie are shown. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 46 (1876), pp. 263-77; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.46 1876
